methopara is stands for METHOd PARAmeters.

INSTALL:
  
  sudo gem install methopara --source http://merbi.st

REQUIREMENT:

  Ruby-1.9.1 only.

USAGE:

  >> require "rubygems"
  >> require "methopara"
  >> def foo(a,b=nil,&c) end
  >> method(:foo).parameters
  => [[:req, :a], [:opt, :b], [:block, :c]]
